        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Restricting the Use of Solitary Confinement Act</b></p> <p>This bill imposes restrictions on the use of solitary confinement for inmates in federal custody.</p> <p>Among the restrictions, the bill prohibits placement in solitary confinement for nondisciplinary reasons; it limits the duration of such placement; and it provides an administrative review process for inmates to contest such placement.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
